item.description:
Nodejs 的 ArrayBuffeer大小端序转换：
https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView/getUint32
// 创建 ArrayBuffer const buffer = new ArrayBuffer(4); // 赋初始值 var bytes = new Uint32Array(buffer) bytes[0] = 0x05; bytes[1] = 0x00; bytes[2] = 0x00; bytes[3] = 0x00; // buffer和Dataview const view = new DataView(buffer); // 按小端序取出数据 console.log(&quot;小端序：&quot;+view.getUint32(0, 1)); // 按大端序取出数据 console.log(&quot;大端序：&quot;+ view.getUint32(0, 0));
